      narr:theme "Pilot health requires per-user cohort analysis over time, not aggregate metrics" ;
      skos:broader narr:AdoptionKPIs ;
      skos:note "Aggregate metrics inherit the heaviest user's shape and hide whether a durable core of habitual users is forming and whether early-trial users are quietly attriting. The methodological principle: analyze per-user over time, never in aggregate." .

